```
![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/9074425/47841229-e5faa400-ddf3-11e8-96f1-260a2747caac.png)


Or you can do it like this.
或者你也可以优化下写成这样
```
let data = [
    ['time', 'pay', 'income'],
    ['2017/5/3', 43.3, 85.8],
    ['2017/5/4', 83.1, 73.4],
    ['2017/5/5', 86.4, 65.2],
    ['2017/5/6', 72.4, 53.9]
];
let dimensions = data[0];
let timeKey = "time";
let series = [];
dimensions.forEach(item => {
    if(item != timeKey){
        series.push({
            type: 'line',
            name:item,
            encode:{
                x:timeKey,
                y:item
            }
        });
    }
})
option = {
    legend: {},
    tooltip: {},
    dataset: {
        source: data
    },
    xAxis: {type: 'time'},
    yAxis: {},
    series: series
}
```
